CustomField.inlineHelpText:
The fully qualified API name (including namespace, if applicable) of the apex class used by the Garbage Collector framework for logging purposes. This apex class must have a public 0-argument constructor, and must implement the GarbageCollectorLogs.Adapter interface. 

This interface has two required methods:
- void log(System.LoggingLevel level, Object message);
- void save();

When left blank, or when no settings are defined, the application will print to traditional debug logs by default.
